## Role Hierarchy

```
CEO
 └─ VP HR
     └─ HR Manager
         ├─ Senior Recruiter
         │   └─ Recruiter
         └─ Interview Panel Lead
             └─ Interviewer
```

---

## Roles Table

| Role | Parent | Access |
|------|--------|--------|
| CEO | — | All records |
| VP HR | CEO | All HR records |
| HR Manager | VP HR | All recruitment records |
| Senior Recruiter | HR Manager | Team's records |
| Recruiter | Senior Recruiter | Own records |
| Interview Panel Lead | HR Manager | Team interview records |
| Interviewer | Interview Panel Lead | Assigned interviews |

---

## HR_Manager.role-meta.xml

```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<Role xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <name>HR Manager</name>
    <parentRole>VP_HR</parentRole>
    <mayForecastManagerShare>false</mayForecastManagerShare>
    <opportunityAccessLevel>Edit</opportunityAccessLevel>
</Role>
```

---

## VP_HR.role-meta.xml

```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<Role xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <name>VP HR</name>
    <parentRole>CEO</parentRole>
    <mayForecastManagerShare>true</mayForecastManagerShare>
    <opportunityAccessLevel>Edit</opportunityAccessLevel>
</Role>
```

---

## Recruiter.role-meta.xml

```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<Role xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <name>Recruiter</name>
    <parentRole>Senior_Recruiter</parentRole>
    <opportunityAccessLevel>Edit</opportunityAccessLevel>
</Role>
```

---

## Org-Wide Defaults (OWD)

| Object | Internal Access |
|--------|-----------------|
| Job__c | Public Read/Write |
| Candidate__c | Private |
| Application__c | Controlled by Parent |
| Interview__c | Controlled by Parent |
| Offer__c | Private |

---

## Sharing Rules

### Candidate Sharing Rule
- **Name:** Share Candidates with HR Team
- **Type:** Criteria-based
- **Criteria:** `Created_By.Department = 'HR'`
- **Share With:** Public Group \"HR Team\"
- **Access:** Read/Write

### Offer Sharing Rule
- **Name:** Share Offers with HR Manager
- **Criteria:** `Status__c = 'Pending'`
- **Share With:** Role \"HR Manager\"
- **Access:** Read/Write

---

## Setup Path
**Setup → Users → Roles → Set Up Roles**




